a Tolstostvol’naya’ and S. ‘Oranzhevaya Tonkostvol’naya’) clones listed in this cross. The flowering of the male cultivars is profuse and spectacular. S. ‘Lyubimets’, S. ‘Oranzhevaya Tonkostvol’naya’ and S. ‘Strela Kupidona’ have thinner stems than S. ‘Oranzhevaya Tolstostvol’naya’. 	V.I. Shaburov 	A.M. Marchenko	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Standard: WSY (WSY0108928, WSY0108929, WSY0108930); duplicate: USNA (NA-0102519, NA-0102520, NA-0102521) and MHA	Established	\N	\N	\N
